               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām “Miracles of Mary" (fols. 1ra-64va)&#xD;
I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fol. 7ra-12ra)&#xD;
I-2) Introductory exhortation and hymns (fols. 12ra-15rb)&#xD;
I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki ... “I worship Thee ...” (fols. 3ra-rb, 4ra-va, 15va-vb)&#xD;
I-4) Taʾāmra Māryām “Miracles of Mary”: 54 miracles (fols. 1ra-2vb, 3va-vb, 5ra-vb, 6ra-vb, 16ra-64va)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>The correct order of fols. 1-16 is as follows:</note>
                     <note>Text I-3: <locus target="#15va">15va-</locus>vb, 4ra-va, 3ra-rb;</note>
                     <note>Text I-4 (miracles 1-4): <locus target="#3va">3va-</locus>vb,1ra-2va, 6ra-vb, 5ra-vb, 16ra.</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>The Miracles of Mary (Text I-4) are numbered.</note>
                  </msItem>
